Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.86,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,欸… 欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.86,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,來 來 來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.86,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.37,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,阿爾法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:13.85,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,希妲製作了鰻當勞的新口味漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.85,0:00:16.02,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,我知道 所以來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:19.47,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,阿爾法大人真的很喜歡鰻當勞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:22.53,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,是呢 他也很喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.56,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,但是這個實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.34,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,實在太革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.56,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:33.25,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,至今希妲開發出的新產品都很成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:36.52,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,無論是夾入炭燒黃瓜的漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.41,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,還是奶油炸肉餅漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.58,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,其創新及全新的美味 都獲得了高銷量和廣泛好評
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:44.21,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,Ｖ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.66,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,但是這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:48.18,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,這次說實話真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.57,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,希妲 說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.33,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,將漢堡的概念 顛覆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:54.43,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,概念？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:58.34,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,將主料用麵包包裹這點對調
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.31,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:02.01,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,用鮪魚替換麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:02.82,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.92,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,不是包裹主食 而是用主食來包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.56,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.08,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,阿爾法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:11.95,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,漢堡因為使用麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:14.12,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,所以卡路里一定會很高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.01,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,如果要發展女性顧客的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.98,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,使用主料的漢堡我覺得也挺有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:21.69,Default,Gamma,0,0,0,,確實有道理… 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.64,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,那麼希妲 裡面夾的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.92,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,夾的是… 米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:30.53,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,不錯啊 感覺很配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:34.03,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,但是米飯很燙的話會傳到主料 需要降低溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.84,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,考慮到保存方法 加上醋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:38.85,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,醬料打算用什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.39,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,和風 醬油最佳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:45.93,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,嗯 還缺最後的點睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.01,Default,Eta,0,0,0,,山葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:50.25,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,完美 然後就是取名了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.19,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,簡單的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.86,Default,Alpha,425,0,0,,{\an1}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.86,Default,Eta,0,290,0,,{\an3}嗯…
